{"tid":2379092,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung Galaxy 集中討論區 (114)  S21 1月29日 公開發售 白卡(𨶙狗藍們)勿入","createTime":"2021-01-25T04:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T13:22:27.000Z","uid":376680,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c23c1e9035f1bd37c0a85dc45377ab148fd559a0","tid":2379092,"uid":376680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://9to5google.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2020/12/samsung_galaxy_s20_ap_1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F9to5google.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F4%2F2020%2F12%2Fsamsung_galaxy_s20_ap_1.gif&h=8b1728eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/thematridox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/samsung_galaxy_s21_ultra_668_leak.gif?fit=668%2C376&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fthematridox.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2Fsamsung_galaxy_s21_ultra_668_leak.gif%3Ffit%3D668%252C376%26ssl%3D1&h=6496c3e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nS21系列已發佈 傳27號派貨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fjh0gXV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffjh0gXV.gif&h=13131abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sc14JDc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsc14JDc.jpg&h=3334b419&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bdVMWYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbdVMWYa.jpg&h=a1a52ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/238kgjs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F238kgjs.gif&h=751ee7ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rxD6VSs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrxD6VSs.gif&h=f92afd8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6DDHuBB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6DDHuBB.gif&h=c61e1547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ciShiu0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FciShiu0.gif&h=f64f4a08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KaoDNop.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKaoDNop.gif&h=72268bb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為120hz重寫動畫 跟手流暢優雅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQCeLyP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQCeLyP.gif&h=11031d8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全面屏窄框開孔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3YNm91c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3YNm91c.gif&h=d41e0c8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n續航：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ww1WxwL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fww1WxwL.jpg&h=ccfcd99f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新機建議設定：<br />\n120Hz+App Booster+手勢操作及隱藏手勢條+封鎖白卡<br />\n<br />\nGalaxy Labs集成系統優化。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">App Booster 提升App性能15%+5% 必裝！</span><br />\n(需直接裝2個apk 因香港未推）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sammobile.com/news/samsung-galaxy-labs-suite-of-apps-let-you-optimize-your-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sammobile.com%2Fnews%2Fsamsung-galaxy-labs-suite-of-apps-let-you-optimize-your-phone%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=b54b4c01\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sammobile.com/news/samsung-galaxy-labs-suite-of-apps-let-you-optimize-your-phone/</a><br />\n<br />\n側邊手勢操作<br />\none hand operation<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.samsung.android.sidegesturepad\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.samsung.android.sidegesturepad&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=6c877a05\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.samsung.android.sidegesturepad</a><br />\n<br />\n安全資料夾（勁有用）X 安全晶片<br />\n<br />\n利用國防級的 Samsung Knox 安全平台，在您的三星手機上<span class=\"red\">打造一個私人的加密空間</span>。移至安全資料夾的<span class=\"red\">應用程序和數據</span>在設備中處於隔離的沙箱中，更可通過公共網絡安全瀏覽的Secure Wi-Fi以及可在設備被盜時遠程屏蔽的Find My Mobile等。其最新的Galaxy S20部件配備了安全晶片S3K250AF，。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.samsung.com/tw/三星發表業界最強行動裝置資料安全晶片解決方案\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.samsung.com%2Ftw%2F%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E8%A3%9D%E7%BD%AE%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=7fc122c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.samsung.com/tw/三星發表業界最強行動裝置資料安全晶片解決方案</a><br />\n<br />\n※ 設備中打造一個獨立的隔離環境。移動或添加至安全文件夾的應用程序和數據 (例如照片、音頻文件、電影文件和文檔) 將無法從安全文件夾外部訪問，無論是 USB 還是 Wi-Fi 直連都不可以。如果您的移動設備檢測到任何Root 權限獲取或ROM 自定義操作，為防止未授權的訪問，安全文件夾將自動鎖定，這種情況下，您將無法再訪問或使用安全文件夾中的內容。<br />\n<br />\n安全資料夾操作邏輯<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dVPvSOleYxU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdVPvSOleYxU&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=597f4837\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dVPvSOleYxU</a><br />\n\t<br />\n <br />\n <br />\nSmart Octopus<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCAHotc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCAHotc.gif&h=0cd5fc8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n指紋錄入竅門<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=woTSMD0FAFk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwoTSMD0FAFk&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=346b1a65\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=woTSMD0FAFk</a><br />\n\t<br />\n <br />\n跟足呢兩條片Set 指紋真係秒解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文字版:<br />\n1)左右拇指喺同一個指紋profile度交替咁錄<br />\n2)再重覆錄多個profile<br />\n3)喺Optimize battery 優化電池使用量閂咗com.samsung.android.biometric<br />\n唔怕裸機就搣埋張mon貼<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n白卡勿入<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/60nPake.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F60nPake.gif&h=a9c46b67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">介紹返手機台嘅過街老鼠 人稱白卡</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WGhDRre.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWGhDRre.jpg&h=64f62114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">唯一各大</span>品牌集中帖不受歡迎人物<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z5Dr0jA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ5Dr0jA.jpg&h=6b76d72e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nProfile:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/255744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/255744</a><br />\n<br />\n站務台：<br />\n強烈建議admin永久封鎖會員 任何淫#255744<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1958035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1958035</a><br />\n--<br />\n點解千祈唔好用3星? <br />\n<br />\n【震】三星手機系統級每分鐘偷連QQ及百度 三星DNS事件誤導用家？（3）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2246699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2246699</a>"},{"pid":"8224e77fb90190b3945232eb38f89ce0990f8a79","tid":2379092,"uid":46085,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6132af65818c5acd367005f5eacdea25337550a2","tid":2379092,"uid":64745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8224e77fb90190b3945232eb38f89ce0990f8a79","tid":2379092,"uid":46085,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:36:39.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=